Enable transition between steps of Sequence.

No parallel conditions. If neccessary > for each condition its own network (Active step / conditions / step change). This also solves jumps. No "active" parts in step. So no timers, counters, comparators etc. those belong to Creating conditions section or outside this block. Only simple bool conditions. Always reset TB1_TransitionEnable bit. This will make sure on PLC cycle only one step of sequence will be processed. Last step/network should be that if active step number is bigger then last used one go to zero step.
Step 3 -> Step 4 - put parts to station 150 / 170
Step 6 and up -> Step 0 - All not used steps go to Init
